  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tricky Typing is a multiplayer typing game where your only input device is a controller. That's right! Each action ranging from a button press to the flick of a joystick is mapped to a letter from A - Z. Play by yourself or with up to 3 other friends as your typing skills are put to the TEST in this Extravaganza >:)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/d2f1be6a58f5dd3f098c0da3b2a52901.poster.avif?t=1770329470\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/d2f1be6a58f5dd3f098c0da3b2a52901.webm?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/d2f1be6a58f5dd3f098c0da3b2a52901.mp4?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Power Ups???</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bobot Mode: Take a second to relax while the game types for you </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/6f01bc38a54055f5f71a1a2ac9264ce0.poster.avif?t=1770329470\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/6f01bc38a54055f5f71a1a2ac9264ce0.webm?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/6f01bc38a54055f5f71a1a2ac9264ce0.mp4?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freeze!: Freeze a random opponent and stop them from being able to type </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/6ad362c0ae64aa1e9acbda0b600493c7.poster.avif?t=1770329470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/6ad362c0ae64aa1e9acbda0b600493c7.webm?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/6ad362c0ae64aa1e9acbda0b600493c7.mp4?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peek-a-Boo <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/fb2fd1b739f75417a1b6dcee204fc384.webp?t=1770329470\" width=20 height=20 /></span> : Place your hands over your opponent’s eyes to temporarily blind them</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/3adaa62c9bc3a5b6da4b85f069b66254.poster.avif?t=1770329470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/3adaa62c9bc3a5b6da4b85f069b66254.webm?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/3adaa62c9bc3a5b6da4b85f069b66254.mp4?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Big Streaks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rack up Streaks so high that they start covering your screen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/54bb66547029193f7dd0b8b3fc954236.poster.avif?t=1770329470\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/54bb66547029193f7dd0b8b3fc954236.webm?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1453160/extras/54bb66547029193f7dd0b8b3fc954236.mp4?t=1770329470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable Dictionary: Start a match off with your own personally submitted words</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dyslexic Font: If you have dyslexia, then the included font, <i>Open Dyslexic</i>, may be for YOU!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjustable Game Speed: Whether at half speed or 150%, play the game how you want to</p></li></ul>",
